net.kebernet.skillz.annotation

Annotation Type Slot


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Inherited
 @Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface Slot
    Marks a method parameter as being populated from a slot value.

    If a parameter is not of a type String then Skillz will use the Coercion class to attempt to convert it to the appropriate value.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.String name
      The name of the slot to read the parameter value from.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      java.lang.String type
      The type of the slot.

    • Element Detail

      • name

        public abstract java.lang.String name
        The name of the slot to read the parameter value from.
        Returns:
        The name of the slot.

      • type

        public abstract java.lang.String type
        The type of the slot. This value is not used at runtime, but will be used to generate the intents.json structure.
        Returns:
        The type of the slot.
        Default:
        ""
